title: Cyril Ramaphosa bangs gavel to close G20 summit after US handover row
summary: South Africa has declined a proposal from the United States, which is set to host the next summit, for the South African president to transfer authority to an embassy official. The rejection highlights tensions between the two nations regarding the summit's organization and leadership. This decision underscores South Africa's desire to maintain its sovereignty and decision-making power in international affairs.

title: I Dream of Theresa May review – willing immigrant’s political conversion spurs stiff debate
summary: A young gay Indian man experiences a phantom vision of a Tory politician, which teaches him about Britishness. However, the story is more of a light-hearted exploration rather than a biting satire. The narrative offers a unique perspective on identity and cultural assimilation.
